<expan>Andr<ex>es</ex></expan>
</ab></add>
<expan>ſwerlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_358_r2l10">getan hat / . als wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_358_r2l9">wol </ab></add> cʒü ercʒelen mainen wenn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_358_r2l11">es dar cʒü kümt / yedoch so wöllen wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdıkeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_358_r2l12">des nicht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſagen</expan> / vnd ewr
                        gnade do mit eren / . vnd das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_358_r2l13">
<del rend="strikethrough">alſo </del>
<expan>gütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beſteen laſſen /
                                <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_358_r2l14">frawen tag cʒü Lıechtmeſſe
                                <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd wöllen vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_358_r2l15">des auf <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> teil vnd
